蔡淑嫻5月時表示，每個口罩成本價30至40元。按此推估，900萬個口罩涉及2億多元，但政府卻在防疫抗疫基金預留了8億元。被問到公帑預算細項，蔡當時以「未埋數」為由，未有公開。<br />\n眾新聞本周三同時向創科局查詢了開支細項，創科局表示待完成第二輪口罩派發，再經獨立核數師審計帳目後，才一併公開整個項目的開支。創科局並指，HKRITA承辦今次項目屬非牟利和實報實銷性質，沒有收取任何行政費，如實際支出少於政府已發放的金額，HKRITA 會將餘額退還政府，「防疫抗疫基金預留了8億元，但相信『銅芯抗疫口罩+&trade;』的實際支出遠低於此預算。」&nbsp;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"肥肥囉，成本價30蚊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cf34a40553932d1fbf2289cc52a3aac0046a02","tid":2143422,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16567c1427dc75186138e62bbb91bf38e55a1039","tid":2143422,"uid":184756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4db11428ea85f880561472b08d84677785e3153","tid":2143422,"uid":311223,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"正常人係雪中送碳<br />\n<br />\n政府logic 係雪後送碳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:36:53.000Z","msg":"雪後送屎會唔會形容得準啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:38:55.000Z","msg":"巴打形容得好過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8ed81eef15df3cf66b779bad5e2c1277117b57","tid":2143422,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"痾完屎先除褲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28134a07b3fcaeea98fc43f85a1d445a6f61241","tid":2143422,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"垃圾幾時派都係垃圾"},{"pid":"4cf0c540c53bff0843a8d70bae127f3dc9504873","tid":2143422,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"港共都知D垃圾冇撚用"},{"pid":"30fd885cb1aacff561f894f10e02399c36663660","tid":2143422,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cb516a3cc485f8495f74106d6d6bb19a365c81e","tid":2143422,"uid":60524,"like":40,"dislike":0,"scor